      "content": "but \"letting the feeling guide me\" doesn't fix the fact that there's nothing there. it's not just a creative block. it's like the part of me that made me \"me\" is just dead. i'm just a body moving through space, performing these human tasks, but if the art is gone... what is the point of the vessel? if the soul is gone, what am i even doing here?",
